singlefamily22.description: This is a 4 family multifamily building being sold-as is, updates have been made to roof and first floor unit. Unit 1 is vacant, Unit 1B, 2, 3 all have tenants with TAW contracts. Please attend the Group Showing on Thursdays from 5-6pm. The property is in the Main South/ Clark University Neighborhood; it's eligible for the University Tuition-Free Program for children in the neighborhood; it is eligible for City of Worcester Lead Abate Program; and it is in an Opportunity Zone eligible area. All are welcome! It is FHA-eligible, Unit 1 will be delivered vacant. All are welcome to attend the Group Showing Open House session. .

Excellent location for commuter access. Less than 1/2 mile walk to Union Station. Steps away from Shrewsbury Street's 'Restaurant Row', and the general Downtown area is near. 1st floor unit has recently been redone; very comfortable & spacious 1 BD studio-like apt. 2nd floor unit is comprised of 2 floors, including finished attic space; its main floor has a huge, updated kitchen, back door leads to a covered deck, with views of Shrewsbury St; there is opportunity in this unit to create your own unique space. Add a staircase to access finished attic, where steep "ladder steps" formerly were. You must see this space to really visualize potential, in this vacant unit. New circuit panels, recent roof, steel beam in basement, and more. Nice flat, fenced in lot, recently groomed to dirt; great potential for off street parking. Also zoned BG-2, in a commercial overlay zone. Great access, mortgage helper, biz op. Must see property, in growing area! Motivated Seller's, make appt.

Open house, broker's open house & group showing on Saturday, 01/28/23 from 1-1:15. Nice turnkey 2 family with separate utilities, and vinyl siding, Both units are 5 rooms, 2 bedrooms, and 1 bath. Large level yard with plenty of off street parking and easy highway access. Long term tenants with rents of $900. Rents have not been raised in many years and could be $1200-1400 as is, or even higher if the kitchens and baths are updated. There are 2 updated gas fired boilers, 2 gas fired hot water tanks, 2 updated 100 amp electrical services with circuit breakers, and a 2 year old roof.

Buyer's financing fell through. Located near route 146 and 290, solid, fully occupied 3-family with 2 bedroom, large living room and kitchen. Newer Pergo flooring in unit 3. Circuit breakers with individual meters.  Spacious manageable back yard, driveway can fit up to 3 vehicles.

Great location. Close to Hospitals, Schools, Highway and lots of local shops. Must see to appreciate. New viewing times available. Home will be delivered vacant when sold.This 2 family home has been in the family for more than 30 years. A little TLC will make this home shine. 10 Rooms, 4 Bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms. Hardwood floors in living dining and bedrooms with linoleum flooring in Kitchens. First floor has gas stove while the 2nd floor has electric stove.  Each floor has storage in hallway with laundry hook ups. Each floor has it's own balcony with lots of space to lounge on the sunny side of house over looking small sitting area that boast many flowers as well as a great spot to barbecue. Large back yard with raised beds for additional gardening.

Renovated Worcester three family in great location!! Level lot with plenty of parking, highway access and close to Polar Park.  The property was extensively renovated approximately ten years ago after a small fire.  All apartments were renovated and updated.  Updated kitchens, baths, cosmetics (hardwood floors) , heat, electric, plumbing, windows, roof, etc.  Each unit is five rooms, three bedrooms, kitchen, living room and a full bath with laundry.  Property has a full sprinkler system. Plenty of off street parking with room for expansion.  The multi is perfect for an owner occupant or investor!!

Cash Cow!!!!!! $5250 monthly income which can be potentially increased to $5800(Since rents are due for raise). Solid Turnkey 3-Family home with great rents and convenient to all area amenities. Close to Polar park Kelly Square. 3/4-bedroom spacious units with good amount of parking. Washer/Dryers in all floors. All 3 Units have long term tenants who pay on time. Lots of improvements done by, new landlord meter, New water heaters, New Boiler. Lead compliance for all 3 units from 2010, foundation resealing, Complete clean up of the yard,1st and second floor upgraded. Tenants pay their own electricity, heater. Sold as-is, where-is. Note: Sellers have never occupied property. Seller make any representations as to the accuracy of any information contained herein. Buyer(s)/buyer agent must conduct their own due diligence, verification(s)

This 2-family home is tucked back on a dead-end street with almost an acre & is perfect for those seeking an Owner Occupant Opportunity! A mudroom/foyer greets you as you enter the first unit. The first-floor unit offers a spacious, open floor plan w/ soaring ceilings, a cabinet packed kitchen featuring s/s appliances, a lg center island w/ pendant lighting, room for a dining table & access to the private back deck. A formal dining rm allows for add’l space for dinner guests. Down the hall is the primary bedrm offering a walk-in closet & full ensuite bath. This unit has 2 add’l bedrms & a full bath w/ marble flooring & laundry. Don’t keep this gem to yourself – private 2nd unit is in the lower level featuring kitchen/dining, a living rm, bedrm w/ ample closet space, a full bath & a bonus rm! Add’l features include a 40x50 detached garage with a half bath, full elec & heat. A stunning in-ground Gunite swimming pool w/ cabana, & an attached 2 car garage! Don't let this gem get away!

Solid 2 family property with a total of 5BR. Owner occupied or investment. Currently 1 vacant unit. Huge garage with loft office in back yard.  There are 2 driveways - one on each side of the building that provides ample parking for both units. Parcel to the right of the building can potentially be subdivided. RL7 zoning  - 2 family allowed and 3 family with special permit. Buyer and buyers' agent to do their own research;

Investors take notice! Redevelopment Opportunity or utilize "As is". Unique opportunity to rehab a distressed 3 family,distressed single famly and a great commercial warehouse.There was a 3 decker that has been torn down between the lot and may have the opportunity to knock down single family and rebuild up to a 6-8 family. This is a tremendous real estate investment opportunity located 26-28-30 Douglas St. Property consists of 3 buildings on 3 separate deeds,1 oversize 3 family with 1400 sq ft.18 rooms, 9 beds, w/d hook ups, oversized baths, each unit is separately metered.1 single family total rehab-2 bed and a large 3600 sq st Commercial Warehouse with offices, reception, 2 baths and 2 large garage bays. Mixed use - Operate your business, plus take additional income from rentals or owner occupied. Property is completely vacant and easy to show! Storage shed can be torn down for additional parking. Bus-line, Park, Holy Cross, Webster square, 290, Mass Pike, & Clark University

Location, Location, Location, steps to the WPI campus is this lovingly restored 2 family property with a detached 2 car garage on an attractive corner lot. Turn-key WPI area investment property.  ZBA approval in hand for expansion to 3 units. 3rd unit could be added in the large walkup attic or alternatively add additional bedrooms for the second-floor unit, (Architectural plans available).  Each existing unit has 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with eat-in kitchens and living space. Fireplaces in both units with beautiful, refinished hardwood floors throughout. Delightful additional sunroom on the first floor.  All separate utilities paid by tenants. Units are all leased to WPI students with a waiting list and with room to increase rents. Come check out this rare opportunity to buy a multifamily property in the WPI community.

UNIQUE AND AMAZING!!!  THIS BEAUTIFUL MULTI-FAMILY HAS 2 SEPARATE HOUSES ON ONE PARCEL.  THE FRONT UNIT HAS 3 LARGE BEDROOMS & 3 FULL BATHS AND EAT-IN KITCHEN WITH SLIDERS TO DECK. THE BACK UNIT HAS 1 BEDROOM & 2 FULL BATHS & LARGE OPEN CONCEPT LIVING/DINING ROOM. CATHEDRAL CEILINGS, TILED BATHROOMS W/JACUZZI SOAKING TUBS, HEATED BIDET TOILETS, DOUBLE SINKS, HANDICAP SHOWER. RECESSED LIGHTING, CROWN MOLDING. GRANITE COUNTERTOPS. WOOD AND TILE FLOORS. WRAPAROUND PORCH, HUGE STONE PATIO, OUTDOOR PIZZA OVEN, SPIRAL STAIRCASE LEADING TO BACK DECK.  3 CAR GARAGE.  LOCATED CLOSE TO MAJOR HIGHWAYS, RESTAURANTS, HOSPITALS, SHOPPING, HANOVER THEATRE, UNIVERSITIES/COLLEGES.

The one you have been waiting for! Investors take note! Completely renovated multi-family for sale in Worcester.  This property is currently vacant making it the perfect opportunity to owner occupy or rent out all three units! Each unit offers bright and sunny eat in kitchens, living rooms, renovated baths, stunning original hardwood floors, new vinyl flooring, and in unit laundry hook ups! 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath in each unit. Front porches on the top two units! Spacious units with convenient layouts. Separate metered utilities. Conveniently located right on Rt 9, in the heart of Worcester. Close to UMASS, Shrewsbury St., Union Station, I-290, I-90 and the Mass Pike!

Nice 3 family off Lincoln Street.  Each floor has 3 bdrm/1 ba with washer/dryer hook-up in every unit.  Nice hardwood floors and trims. 1st and 3rd floor was recently renovated.  1st and 3rd floor is vacant and ready for new owner and tenant.  2nd floor tenant paying $1200 a month but is looking for suitable housing so potential of having all 3 units vacant.  Gas cooking and heating.  Great location near bus lines and shopping.

Now available in the Vernon Hill area of Worcester are these two triple decker homes on one deed!! Front building (17) offers 1-3br per unit, large kitchen and living room. The basement unit and first floor are 1br each. Back building (15): First floor is 2br with baseboard heat. Second floor is 2br and has gas parlor heaters.  Third floor is a 1br unit with central heat by gas. Each unit has kitchen and living rooms.  All separate utilities. Close to Woo Sox Polar Park, Canal District, Quinsigamond Village~~Walmart shopping plaza~~ route 146 and MA Pike.

2-family in quiet neighborhood about 100 yds from lake, yet, walking distance to most anything in Worcester.  Lake view.  Both apartments are in great shape with lots of higher-end upgrades and very nice for rentals.  Move in ready.  All mechanicals, electrical, plumbing, driveway and common areas have either been upgraded/replaced since initial purchase.  Common areas are finished as interiors- not common.  Has a bonus common sunroom and large storage in back that was a fully conditioned attached two car garage if you want to convert it back, it would be simple.  Yard is is easily among nicest in whole neighborhood, flat and private, with a massive amount of plantings that bring waves of color during gardening season.  House is perfect for someone who is looking to start a family in great neighborhood and needs a yard for entertaining or children to play in with total comfort.  Owner bought house for mother over 25yrs ago to make sure she had her rent controlled and she is no longer there.  Wants to see a family move in to a great quiet neighborhood that children will likely benefit most as most things are walking distance.  Great deal.  Similar houses on same street sold for more recently than his asking.

Location! Near WPI & Elm Park. Quiet & safe area off vibrant Park Avenue. Near new Doherty High School. Excellent money maker but new kitchen/bath upgrades will increase income 30%. Great opportunity in a good area.

High Revenue Generated Income Property! This Rare Commercial/Residential Mixed Use Property is in the WPI Location and close to WSU, Assumption College, MCPH, (College Central), Courthouse and Union Station-Train Station. All Major Rtes. 290, 190, Rte 20, 146 &122 as well as Worcester Airport operated by Mass Port. A very well maintained 4 unit- the property currently generates $120,792.00 with an additional income available from a finished office space in lower level that is carpeted, HVAC, plastered walls and full tiled bathroom. The Commercial unit is leased by a Dental Office on 64 Highland Street with 3 yrs. remaining on the lease and an option to renew the Dental Office Lease. All 3 apartments are leased (TAW) and have wonderful tenants. Location is on the corner of Highland and Dean Street, Location is everything!!!Lead Paint Certificates available on all units! Dentist is triple net rent!

Think spring time to start making plans Location Up and coming area new homes ready to go so make it happen .Builders /Investors plans for lot split there are 4 extra lots time to start building the time is now to get started. Look pictures and registry of deeds lot plans looking for quite area with new homes .Units will be delivered vacant upon sale .Note:*11 Svenson Ave is included in sale ! that's extra 7100 sq. Great commuter location minutes to146, Rt 20,Mass Pike and Ball Park on dead end street back yard abutting Audubon land for privacy .Lg 2 Family with 3 bed in each unit and laundry off street parking garage for 1 .Second has a walk up attic with extra for storage or your creative touch!  2 car detached garage.  Plans for 3 other lots on 15, lot a 11 Svenson for a total of 4 extra lots plus the main house lot! Think of the future Owner wants to sell as one package let make a deal bring an offer.  Title 5 in hand , Don't miss out on this s great opportunity for an investment

Location, Location, Location. Well maintained beautiful three family. Move in condition. Great opportunity for an owner occupant or investment. Roof is 4 year old and heat system for the first floor is 1 year old. Fenced backyard and nice garage. Rents are below market. Few minutes away from Worcester State University. Quick access to routes 9, 12, 122 and 290.

Incredible opportunity to own this 4-unit mixed use building! CASH COW. The majority of the work has been done for you! Two of the three apartments have been renovated. The bar is a classic that can not be replicated. Ready to operate or lease for additional income! Conveniently located near many city landmarks--Polar Park, Union Station, Holy Cross, Clark University and major routes--290, Mass Pike, and 146. The area offers tons of potential to fill these units and increase your income as well as build your portfolio! Group showings Thursday 11/3 5-6pm

Well maintained 3 unit building on Millbury St.  First floor is restaurant/bar.  Second floor unit is 3 bedrooms, 1 bath and third floor is 2 bedrooms, 1 bath.  Tenants are long term and TAW.  Bar and bottom apartment are gas heat.  Top apartment is electric.  Circuit breakers throughout. New windows, siding, roof, fire escape and driveway all redone in 2016.  A/C unit for bar is 3 years old. Near Polar park with access to 146 and 290.

Sign up to be notified of the next group tour.  Please email agent if you intend to come.  No Walk-ins. Wonderfull west side 3 family with ample parking.  Perfect low touch investor property.  NO WORK TO DO, just collect the rents.  Extensive renovations in 2017 which included: New Roof(roof was removed, re-framed and replaced, (check out the attic photo-all new wood) New Windows, New electrical, new services and sub panels in each unit, Granite kitchens, new bathrooms, 2 new Forced hot air heating systems(2nd in unit and 3rd in attic), extensive plumbing upgrades.  Additional space in basement as well.  All rents are below market which should be $1900-2000 per unit.  Washers and dryers for each unit.

This solid and well maintained 3 family property is in perfect for first Buyer or an Investor.  Property features an open floor plan. Each unit has 3 spacious bedrooms with washer and dryer hook-ups. Sprinkler system have been installed.  There is parking for 4 cars and conveniently location near the Polar Park Stadium in Kelly Square . Also close proximity to schools, shopping and Rt-290 and  Rt-146. Rents are below market and have TAW.  First showing at Open house on Sunday 9-18-2022 from 1:00 p.m. to 3:30 p.m..

PRICE ADJUSTMENT! Investors or first-time home buyers, dont miss this opportunity for this 3-FAMILY multi is perfect as it resides in a highly desirable area of Worcester, right on the border of Shrewsbury. This property has a total of 12 rooms, 6 bedrooms and 3 full baths plus a finished basement! There's plenty of room to grow and add more value for great immediate value! In addition to all of that, LOCATION! With close proximity to the highway, this makes it easy to travel to Boston and other major areas. Hospitals, restaurants, shopping and schools all nearby at your convenience. This home Has ample off-street parking available. Rents are below market, units are TAW. 24 hour notice needed but available to show immediately.

Excellent large 9 BR investment property fully occupied and rented. Close to Holy Cross and ballpark.  Many updates within the 1st, 2nd and 3rd floor units, such as kitchen flooring, paint, vanity, lighting, and carpet. TAW tenants paying below market rents due to long-term tenants. Close to 290 and 146. Possibility for 4-6 parkings. Large yard. Updated electric system with breaker boxes in every unit, replacement windows and a 7 year old roof. Quit residential family neighborhood. Well maintained.
